e começou a conversar.

744
00:41:59,266 --> 00:42:00,392
Talvez Gail.

745
00:42:00,476 --> 00:42:01,435
Sim, senhor.

746
00:42:01,519 --> 00:42:02,811
Era bem simpática.

747
